WEBVTT

00:03:59.167 --> 00:04:01.824
for the benefit of nondisabled people.

00:04:01.824 --> 00:04:03.952
The purpose of these images

00:04:03.952 --> 00:04:07.763
is to inspire you, to motivate you,

00:04:07.763 --> 00:04:09.838
so that we can look at them

00:04:09.838 --> 00:04:12.927
and think, "Well, however bad my life is,

00:04:12.927 --> 00:04:14.958
it could be worse.

00:04:14.958 --> 00:04:18.286
I could be that person."

00:04:18.286 --> 00:04:21.662
But what if you are that person?

00:04:21.662 --> 00:04:23.750
I've lost count of the number of times that I've

00:04:23.750 --> 00:04:26.218
been approached by strangers

00:04:26.218 --> 00:04:29.123
wanting to tell me that they think I'm brave

00:04:29.123 --> 00:04:30.880
or inspirational,